            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2031%3A1-32%3A32%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_1%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3EEzekiel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EEgypt%20Compared%20to%20Fallen%20Assyria%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20June%26%23xA0%3B21%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E31%3A1%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EOn%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20third%20month%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20ancient%20Hebrew%20lunar%20calendar.%20This%20event%20occurred%20on%20June%26%23xA0%3B21%2C%20587%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3B%20also%20see%20note%20on%201%3A1.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20during%20the%20eleventh%20year%20of%20King%20Jehoiachin%26%23x2019%3Bs%20captivity%2C%20this%20message%20came%20to%20me%20from%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3A%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_2%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BSon%20of%20man%2C%20give%20this%20message%20to%20Pharaoh%2C%20king%20of%20Egypt%2C%20and%20all%20his%20hordes%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BTo%20whom%20would%20you%20compare%20your%20greatness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_3%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20are%20like%20mighty%20Assyria%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewhich%20was%20once%20like%20a%20cedar%20of%20Lebanon%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ewith%20beautiful%20branches%20that%20cast%20deep%20forest%20shade%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20with%20its%20top%20high%20among%20the%20clouds.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_4%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EDeep%20springs%20watered%20it%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20helped%20it%20to%20grow%20tall%20and%20luxuriant.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThe%20water%20flowed%20around%20it%20like%20a%20river%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Estreaming%20to%20all%20the%20trees%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_5%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20great%20tree%20towered%20high%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ehigher%20than%20all%20the%20other%20trees%20around%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EIt%20prospered%20and%20grew%20long%20thick%20branches%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ebecause%20of%20all%20the%20water%20at%20its%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_6%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20birds%20nested%20in%20its%20branches%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20in%20its%20shade%20all%20the%20wild%20animals%20gave%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EAll%20the%20great%20nations%20of%20the%20world%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Elived%20in%20its%20shadow.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_7%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EIt%20was%20strong%20and%20beautiful%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ewith%20wide-spreading%20branches%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Efor%20its%20roots%20went%20deep%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Einto%20abundant%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_8%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3ENo%20other%20cedar%20in%20the%20garden%20of%20God%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecould%20rival%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ENo%20cypress%20had%20branches%20to%20equal%20it%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eno%20plane%20tree%20had%20boughs%20to%20compare.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3ENo%20tree%20in%20the%20garden%20of%20God%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ecame%20close%20to%20it%20in%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_9%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EBecause%20I%20made%20this%20tree%20so%20beautiful%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20gave%20it%20such%20magnificent%20foliage%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Eit%20was%20the%20envy%20of%20all%20the%20other%20trees%20of%20Eden%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ethe%20garden%20of%20God.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_10%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BTherefore%2C%20this%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20Because%20Egypt%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E31%3A10%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eyou.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20became%20proud%20and%20arrogant%2C%20and%20because%20it%20set%20itself%20so%20high%20above%20the%20others%2C%20with%20its%20top%20reaching%20to%20the%20clouds%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_11%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20a%20mighty%20nation%20that%20will%20destroy%20it%20as%20its%20wickedness%20deserves.%20I%20have%20already%20discarded%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_12%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20foreign%20army%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20terror%20of%20the%20nations%26%23x2014%3Bhas%20cut%20it%20down%20and%20left%20it%20fallen%20on%20the%20ground.%20Its%20branches%20are%20scattered%20across%20the%20mountains%20and%20valleys%20and%20ravines%20of%20the%20land.%20All%20those%20who%20lived%20in%20its%20shadow%20have%20gone%20away%20and%20left%20it%20lying%20there.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_13%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThe%20birds%20roost%20on%20its%20fallen%20trunk%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20the%20wild%20animals%20lie%20among%20its%20branches.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_14%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1-vn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ELet%20the%20tree%20of%20no%20other%20nation%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eproudly%20exult%20in%20its%20own%20prosperity%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3Ethough%20it%20be%20higher%20than%20the%20clouds%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eand%20it%20be%20watered%20from%20the%20depths.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EFor%20all%20are%20doomed%20to%20die%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Eto%20go%20down%20to%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet1%22%3EThey%20will%20land%20in%20the%20pit%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22poet2%22%3Ealong%20with%20everyone%20else%20on%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_15%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20says%3A%20When%20Assyria%20went%20down%20to%20the%20grave%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E31%3A15%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Eto%20Sheol%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2031%3A16%2C%2017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20I%20made%20the%20deep%20springs%20mourn.%20I%20stopped%20its%20rivers%20and%20dried%20up%20its%20abundant%20water.%20I%20clothed%20Lebanon%20in%20black%20and%20caused%20the%20trees%20of%20the%20field%20to%20wilt.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_16%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20made%20the%20nations%20shake%20with%20fear%20at%20the%20sound%20of%20its%20fall%2C%20for%20I%20sent%20it%20down%20to%20the%20grave%20with%20all%20the%20others%20who%20descend%20to%20the%20pit.%20And%20all%20the%20other%20proud%20trees%20of%20Eden%2C%20the%20most%20beautiful%20and%20the%20best%20of%20Lebanon%2C%20the%20ones%20whose%20roots%20went%20deep%20into%20the%20water%2C%20took%20comfort%20to%20find%20it%20there%20with%20them%20in%20the%20depths%20of%20the%20earth.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_31_17%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2231%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EIts%20allies%2C%20too%2C%20were%20all%20destroyed%20and%20had%20passed%20away.%20They%20had%20gone%20down%20to%20the%20grave%26%23x2014%3Ball%20those%20nations%20that%20had%20lived%20in%20its%20shade.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22e